nodes.text: The Executor I-class Star Dreadnought was a model of Executor-class Star Dreadnought used by the Imperial Navy during the Imperial Era. At one point, one such Star Dreadnought flew over a cloudy, white celestial body, while flanked by multiple Imperial-class Star Destroyers. The model was propelled by red-hued engines and was succeeded by the Executor II-class Star Dreadnought.
The Executor I-class Star Dreadnought was mentioned on a card of the same name in the 2019 Super Star Destroyer Expansion Pack by Fantasy Flight Games, for the miniatures game Star Wars: Armada.
